     Author: Derek Tremblay (derektremblay666@gmail.com)
     Contributors: Claude (Anthropic)
     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Matrix / Terminal theme.
         CRT phosphor-screen aesthetic: pure black (#000000) background
         with matrix-green (#00FF41) text. Hacker aesthetic, perfect for
         hex editing and reverse engineering sessions.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in MatrixTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

